Mu 1994, mvita eyi yakafikisha ku dienza dia République de Transnistrie mu tshitupa tshia ku est kua Moldavie, ditunga didi ne mbulamatadi ne makuta adi ditunga nansha dimue dia mu ONU kadiyi dianyisha.
