Bisamba bia bungi bia pa buloba bujima bia bena Kristo ne bia badi kabayi bena Kristo mbipete bilele bia bungi bidi bitangila tshikondo tshia kuikisha.
Bantu batu ne tshilele tshia kubenga kulala butuku bua muladilu wa dituku dia kumpala dia Pasaka.
Kudi mishindu ya bungi ya buena Kristo idibu bumvuija tshilele etshi, kadi tshidi mua kuikala tshilele tshia bantu ba bisamba bia bende kumpala kua bena Kristo tshia kulela.
Bitendelelu bia bungi bia bena Katolike bitu bienza Pasaka mu Disambombo dilolo mu tshikondo tshia dikudimuka dia mîdima, padi bisumbu bituadija kuenza Pasaka anu mundankulu bua kusekelela dibika dia Yezu ku lufu.
