Basalayi bavua bavuala bilamba bia mudimu ne bavua babikila bena mudimu nabu ne mêna abu a ku nzubu anyi a miaba ivuabu benza mudimu.
Malanda a ku mudimu mmakole, ne bantu batu batamba kuimanyina pa dienza mudimu pamue pamutu pa kuimanyina pa dianyisha didibu mua kupesha muntu bua mudimu wende anyi bua malu adiye muenze.
Bavua balomba bena mudimu bua bitabe mapangadika onso avuabu bangata, ne bavua babalomba bua batumikile bamfumu babu kabayi badiabakena.
